msgctxt "Talk_001"
msgid ""
"<1.so>The temperature in the <2.se_co>Gerudo Desert<3.re_co>\n"
"swings dramatically between the day and\n"
"night.\n"
"If you haven't got the right clothing for\n"
"hot and cold weather, your health will\n"
"certainly suffer.\n"
"Spend too much time in a temperature\n"
"you can't handle and your goose is\n"
"cooked. <4.pa>Or frozen, I guess.\n"
"<5.so>Even horses don't like going into the\n"
"desert. That really tells you something...\n"
"\n"
"<6.so>And of course, when you add monsters\n"
"to that mix... It's just a nightmare of a\n"
"place.\n"
"<7.so>That's what got me thinking that having a\n"
"<8.se_co>legendary sword<9.re_co> would make a serious\n"
"difference. I'd be safe with that.<10.ch>"
msgstr ""

