msgctxt "Talk_009"
msgid ""
"<1.so>You've never heard of the <2.se_co>legendary\n"
"sword<3.re_co>? The one that can only be wielded\n"
"by the chosen hero? Weird...\n"
"Well, personally, I think it must be in the\n"
"<4.se_co>Great Hyrule Forest <5.re_co>in the Eldin region.\n"
"\n"
"I mean, the whole reason they call it the\n"
"<6.se_co>Lost Woods <7.re_co>is because you always lose\n"
"your way and end up back at the start.\n"
"If someone wanted to hide a <8.se_co>legendary\n"
"sword<9.re_co>, is there really a better place than\n"
"that to do it?\n"
"But I get lost in the woods without magic\n"
"making it happen, so there's no way I'm\n"
"going in there."
