msgid ""
"I want to go to the <1.se_co>Gerudo Desert<2.re_co>, but...\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"It gets <3.se_co>scorching hot<4.re_co> during the day and\n"
"<5.se_co>freezing cold<6.re_co> at night. And then there are\n"
"all the monsters to worry about, too...\n"
"<7.so>If you dress right, you can mitigate\n"
"how much the climate affects you,\n"
"of course.\n"
"But with the gear I've got, those\n"
"monsters would have me for lunch faster\n"
"than you can say, \"<8.pa>AHHHHHHHHHHHH!\"\n"
